name: Set Collector Configuration
description:
ADVANCED SCRIPT - This Remote action should be used by a certified Nexthink expert.
Collector configuration is changed using Nxtcfg tool, except for 'AppStartTime'.
'AppStartTime' configuration parameter change involves Registry Key changes and additional verifications done by the Remote Action.

inputs.description: Optional number to identify the installation (0-2147483647)
inputs.name: Tag

inputs.description: Logging mode (0 - Silent, 1 - Verbose, 2 - Debug). It might impact performance. Use only for debugging
inputs.name: LogMode

inputs.description: List of domains for which to report the URL of web requests (comma-separated)
inputs.name: WMDomains

inputs.description: Enables (1) or disables (0) IOPS monitoring functionality
inputs.name: IOPS

inputs.description: Period, in hours, in which the Collector checks for new installed packages and updates. Integer in range (0-24) (0-Never)
inputs.name: PKGInterval

inputs.description: Enables (0) or disables (1) App Start Time feature. If enabled, a list of executables must be provided as AppStartTimeWhitelist input parameter
inputs.name: AppStartTime

inputs.description: Comma-separated list of executables that should be monitored by Collector. Example":" 'my-executable.exe, exec*.exe, prefix*name*suffix'. Use "*" if you want to monitor all the executables
inputs.name: AppStartTimeWhitelist

inputs.description: Enables (1) or disables (0) the Windows Focus Time Monitoring
inputs.name: WindowFocusTimeMonitoring

inputs.description: Enables (0) or disables (1) the User Interaction Time Monitoring
inputs.name: UserInteractionTimeMonitoring

inputs.description: Enables (1) or disables (0) the Anonymize User Name
inputs.name: AnonymizeUserName

inputs.description: Enables (1) or disables (0) the Anonymize Wifi Networks
inputs.name: AnonymizeWifiNetwork
